entries.body:
Neither the stone nor the bolts of the tomb could hold Christ a captive;

Death lies conquered by him, he has trampled on hell’s fiery chasm.

With him a throng of saints ascended to heavenly regions,

And to many he showed himself, letting them see and touch him.{fn:0} SCENES {fn:0}

Hail! Thou king of all the living;

Hail! Thou judge of all the dead,{fn:0}

At the right hand of thy Father,

Thou art throned in highest power,{fn:1}

And from thence just judge of sinners,

Thou shalt one day come again. HYMN 9, A {fn:0}
